_cooperative projects with industry to reduce 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
emissions from the flexography, lithography, and screen 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
printing sectors of the printing industry; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

